    "shortDescription": "<p>This spell functions like <i><i>symbol of</i> death</i>, except that all creatures within 60 feet of a <i><i>symbol of</i> <i>stunning</i></i> instead become stunned for 1d6 rounds.</p><p><i>Note:</i> Magic traps such as <i><i>symbol of</i> <i>stunning</i></i> are hard to detect and disable. A rogue (only) can use the Perception skill to find a <i><i>symbol of</i> <i>stunning</i></i> and Disable Device to thwart it. The DC in each case is 25 + spell level, or 32 for <i><i>symbol of</i> <i>stunning</i></i>.</p>"
